    <li><strong>Vehicle Type:</strong> Luxury or high-theft cars can increase costs.</li>
    <li><strong>Location:</strong> Urban areas often result in higher insurance rates.</li>
    <li><strong>Coverage Amount:</strong> Higher coverage leads to increased premiums.</li>
