<p>Your driving history significantly impacts your insurance rates. Maintaining a clean driving record without accidents or traffic violations can help lower your premium. Insurance companies reward safe drivers. Consider taking a driver safety course to further impress insurers and potentially earn discounts.</p>
<h3>Utilize Discounts</h3>
